18 Forewarn 3 When it enters a battle, the Pokémon can tell one of the moves an opposing Pokémon has.
36 Anticipation 3 The Pokémon can sense an opposing Pokémon's dangerous moves.
54 Magic Bounce 11 Reflects status moves instead of getting hit by them.
72 Justified 4 Being hit by a Dark-type move boosts the Attack stat of the Pokémon, for justice.
90 Morbid Surge 9 Turns the ground into Morbid Terrain when the Pokémon enters a battle.
100 Moxie 7 The Pokémon shows moxie, and that boosts the Attack stat after knocking out any Pokémon.

Disc Ability Score Description
